snippet.title: Repose - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the twisted trailer for Repose, an upcoming dark exploration/puzzle game from developer Bozó Attila Bertold. In Repose, explore, fight, and maintain a healthy sleep schedule as you descend the twisted levels of the corporation that hired you for unknown reasons.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
